title: DDFP: Talking Quarterbacks with Joe Theismann
itunes:title: DDFP: Talking Quarterbacks with Joe Theismann
description:
Shek & Rank welcome Joe Theismann talk about the good (Aaron Rodgers), the bad (Tony Romo) & the ugly (Brett Favre) of NFL quarterbacking; plus, a visit from Handsome Hank, who reads Favre's incendiary remarks about his successor, then badmouths American snacks; finally, the fellas jump into the DeLorean to see who wins Week 5's biggest games.
